OL,3,CQR code in bars this Christmas to
OL,4,C'discreetly' report suspected drink
OL,5,Cdrivers
OL,7,FThe message not to drink and drive
OL,8,Fthis Christmas has stepped up a gear
OL,9,Fwith new QR codes in pubs and bars
OL,10,Foffering punters a direct line to
OL,11,Fpolice if they suspect someone of
OL,12,Fclimbing behind the wheel.
OL,14,FDurham Constabulary has installed the
OL,15,Fsigns in parts of the force area in a
OL,16,Fbid to combat the issue of drink and
OL,17,Fdrug driving and potentially save
OL,18,Flives this festive season.
