OL,5,Cdrivers
OL,7,FThe QR codes, which are now in every
OL,8,Fpub and bar in Darlington, can be
OL,9,Fscanned with a smart phone to make a
OL,10,Freport to the force.
OL,12,FConstable Lee Blaney, who is behind
OL,13,Fthe scheme told ITV Tyne Tees: "Nine
OL,14,Ftimes out of ten when you're waiting
OL,15,Fat a bar you've got your phone out.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/6
