OL,3,CQR code in bars this Christmas to
OL,4,C'discreetly' report suspected drink
OL,5,Cdrivers
OL,7,F"You're looking for something to do
OL,8,Fand it might just give people that
OL,9,Flittle bit extra idea of - we know
OL,10,Fthat somebody's drink driving, we
OL,11,Fdon't actually have the time or the
OL,12,Fdiscreetness to make a phone call so
OL,13,Fif we can do it ultimately via a text
OL,14,Fmessage exchange, it may well just
OL,15,Fsave one life on our roads."
