OL,3,CQR code in bars this Christmas to
OL,4,C'discreetly' report suspected drink
OL,5,Cdrivers
OL,7,FUsed elsewhere in the country, the
OL,8,Finitiative is a first for the region
OL,9,Fand is being launched in and around
OL,10,FDarlington because it is the area
OL,11,Fwhich saw the highest number of drink
OL,12,Fand drug drivers of anywhere across
OL,13,Fthe force this time last year.
OL,15,FExplaining how it works, PC Blaney
OL,16,Fsaid: "(You) get (your) phone, scan
OL,17,Fthe QR code, click on the live chat
OL,18,Ficon then from there you'll be
OL,19,Fstraight through to a control room
OL,20,Fcall handler.
