OL,5,Cdrivers
OL,7,F"You provide the information of the
OL,8,Fpotential suspect and that information
OL,9,Fwill be disseminated to one of our
OL,10,Froad policing officers who can
OL,11,Fhopefully intercept the individuals
OL,12,Fconcerned."
OL,14,FThe launch has been welcomed by bar
OL,15,Fowner Tori Gill.
OL,17,FShe said: "It's really important for
OL,18,Fus because we want to promote
OL,19,Fresponsible drinking and as part of
OL,20,Four license we have to do that.
